00:49:18.110 --> 00:49:20.960
sometimes falls on deaf ears.

00:49:20.960 --> 00:49:22.880
You have to be relentless.

00:49:22.880 --> 00:49:25.130
If you're not relentless--

00:49:25.130 --> 00:49:27.601
there are so many things
that happen in our society.

00:49:27.601 --> 00:49:28.100
Right?

00:49:28.100 --> 00:49:30.350
It gets published,
and nothing changes,

00:49:30.350 --> 00:49:33.980
until people get up and start
